## Key Features

### 1. Comprehensive Project Management
- **900+ projects** capacity (KPI requirement)
- Full project lifecycle tracking
- Multi-organization partnerships
- Geographic coverage (22 countries, 8 sea basins)
- Budget and timeline management
- Community-led action indicators

### 2. Advanced Categorization
- **7 thematic clusters** (exceeds KPI requirement of 5)
  - Pollution Prevention & Reduction
  - Conservation & Restoration
  - Sustainable Blue Economy
  - Water Management
  - Climate Adaptation & Mitigation
  - Nature-Based Solutions
  - Circular Economy
- Flexible keyword tagging system
- Solution type classification
- EU Directive alignment tracking

### 3. Synergy Documentation
- **10+ synergies** tracking (KPI requirement)
- Multi-project linking
- Synergy type categorization
- Status tracking (Identified → Active → Completed)
- Impact assessment
- Contact management

### 4. Interactive Dashboard Support
- Multi-criteria search capabilities
  - Keyword search
  - Region filtering
  - Cluster filtering
  - Organization filtering
  - Solution type filtering
  - Advanced combinations
- Full-text search optimization
- Usage analytics tracking
- Performance-optimized indexes

### 5. Access Control
- **4 user roles:**
  - Admin (full access)
  - Consortium Partner (edit projects)
  - FSTP Project (edit own projects)
  - Public (read-only)
- Secure password hashing
- Activity logging
- Audit trail

