## Risk Assessment & Mitigation

| Risk | Probability | Impact | Mitigation |
|------|-------------|--------|------------|
| Data migration errors from 2023 Portfolio | Medium | High | Implement validation scripts, manual verification |
| Inconsistent organization naming | High | Medium | Develop naming convention guide, deduplication process |
| Dashboard performance with 900+ projects | Low | High | Indexes optimized, query optimization, caching strategy |
| User adoption of digital tool | Medium | High | Training sessions, user-friendly interface, documentation |
| Data quality from multiple sources | Medium | Medium | Verification workflow, quality checks, admin review |

